# ViewTube — CSV & Analytics Naming Audit

Audit of all CSV header names, metric names, tag types, and CSV-related logic found across 6 old ViewTube repo copies that are missing, incomplete, or not properly wired into the current viewtube production codebase. Organized by category: HEADER_MAP gaps, CSV tag/type names, format-detection column names, Shorts-specific signals, dataPipeline metric references, and API metric names used in old youtubeService versions.

## Comparing old repo copies vs current `/Users/cwb/Downloads/viewtube`

**Repos scanned:** viewtube copy 2, copy 3, copy 4, copy 7, ustube-CHARTS, copy-of-ustube-x  
**Focus:** CSV column names, header maps, metric aliases, tag types, detection logic

---

## ✅ STATUS KEY
- ✅ In current `viewtube` and working
- ⚠️ Partially present (alias missing or mapped wrong)
- ❌ Found in old copies, missing or broken in current

---

